Requirements

Set of rules for the player to follow

The game must have a ending for the player (win/lose)

Player must have a loss conition (0 lives remaining)

Player must have a way to win (guessing number)

Doofus rules

Easy to navigate menu / console

Cards for card game must have correct suit and number

Console / gui must display correct information

Have the option to start a game (start)

Have the option to end the game early (quit)
